Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.21,0:00:09.47,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning, senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.03,0:00:11.69,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.69,0:00:13.24,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Kuroneko?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.14,0:00:16.07,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You enrolled in my school?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.65,0:00:17.41,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.22,0:00:22.40,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Not because of you or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.81,0:00:25.24,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Well yeah, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.24,0:00:26.87,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You should've told me!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.33,0:00:29.37,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I had no obligation to.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.37,0:00:31.99,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What does it have to do with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.99,0:00:32.94,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.15,0:00:35.23,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I think it's great!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.62,0:00:38.91,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get along then, {\i1}kouhai{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.20,0:00:42.15,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed, senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.63,0:00:44.00,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What an idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.66,0:00:49.80,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyou-chan, Kyou-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.80,0:00:52.45,main,,0000,0000,0000,,She's a first year, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.80,0:00:54.03,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know her?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.44,0:00:58.43,main,,0000,0000,0000,,She's a friend of Kirino and mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.06,0:01:01.91,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What's her name?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.91,0:01:03.03,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Kuroneko.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.49,0:01:07.85,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, what's her real name?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,main,,0000,0000,0000,,{There's No Way My Kouhai Can Be This Rotten}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.89,0:02:44.41,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Gokou Ruri.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.41,0:02:47.47,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That would be my human name.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.63,0:02:49.83,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Gokou?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.31,0:02:57.67,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That feels weird...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.67,0:02:59.63,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I called you Kuroneko all this time...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.95,0:03:03.16,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Then continue to do so.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.56,0:03:04.89,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.10,0:03:06.92,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.92,0:03:09.18,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you guys here?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.96,0:03:18.01,main,,0000,0000,0000,,With Miss Kiririn away, you must be so lonely, so I was invited to check in on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.01,0:03:19.90,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Ruri-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.90,0:03:22.15,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Please stop constructing false realities.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.55,0:03:27.34,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Truth is, I'm feeling more refreshed than ever with that noisy sister gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.07,0:03:29.70,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I appreciate the thought, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.36,0:03:31.62,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.62,0:03:33.27,main,,0000,0000,0000,,And you're accepting it without a second thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.46,0:03:43.97,main,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the present you got that one time...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.41,0:03:46.46,main,,0000,0000,0000,,How nostalgic.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.83,0:03:50.71,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hasn't Kirino called you guys or anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.32,0:03:57.95,main,,0000,0000,0000,,She put up a short update on her SNS blog, but that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.92,0:04:02.05,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I was just getting fed up with that woman, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.70,0:04:04.67,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so refreshing to have her gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.55,0:04:10.72,main,,0000,0000,0000,,To be perfectly honest, I'm kind of angry with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.38,0:04:19.02,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I consider her a close friend, and I believed she thought of me the same way...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.32,0:04:23.80,main,,0000,0000,0000,,And yet, taking off like that without consulting any of us...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.80,0:04:26.38,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's really painful, sad, and hard to bear.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.38,0:04:27.21,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.94,0:04:36.24,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I admire that she's following her ambitions like this, but I still can't agree with how she went about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.80,0:04:41.09,main,,0000,0000,0000,,And on top of that, she hasn't called or emailed us,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.09,0:04:44.24,main,,0000,0000,0000,,and I haven't seen her online at all, either...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.66,0:04:48.41,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all slowly getting to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.29,0:04:55.22,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you think it's okay for me to be just a little mad?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.22,0:04:56.00,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.43,0:04:59.34,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.34,0:05:01.27,main,,0000,0000,0000,,How about the three of us go out somewhere then?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.83,0:05:05.00,main,,0000,0000,0000,,And after that, you can post about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.00,0:05:07.76,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll definitely piss her off.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.31,0:05:13.15,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I like that idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.88,0:05:29.68,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you running off home?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.27,0:05:32.48,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I sent you a mail, didn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.48,0:05:34.88,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I said I'd come to your classroom after homeroom's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.52,0:05:38.24,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't remember that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.24,0:05:40.15,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So, who's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.32,0:05:43.57,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to introduce you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.57,0:05:46.79,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Pleased to meet you! I'm Tamura Manami.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.20,0:05:49.43,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Belphegor!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.65,0:05:51.97,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Belphe?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.92,0:05:54.23,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Never mind...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.54,0:05:57.13,main,,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Gokou. Pleased to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.13,0:06:01.17,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyou-chan, you call her Kuroneko-san, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.17,0:06:02.97,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you mind if I did too?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.97,0:06:04.28,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Either way is fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.18,0:06:09.23,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be going then.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.71,0:06:10.65,main,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.65,0:06:11.74,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, wait up!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.27,0:06:16.08,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Maschera's airing today so I have to get back.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.08,0:06:19.29,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Maschera ended at episode 12 in the second season.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.29,0:06:20.79,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It isn't airing anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.79,0:06:22.98,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't talk like it's over!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.56,0:06:24.80,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.80,0:06:28.00,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I just meant to say that the next season hasn't been scheduled yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.60,0:06:31.66,main,,0000,0000,0000,,None of the real fans have given up on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.02,0:06:33.37,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Gokou-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.69,0:06:35.05,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you free?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.05,0:06:37.52,main,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to karaoke, so if you wa—
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.52,0:06:38.63,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not free.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.98,0:06:42.54,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.54,0:06:45.48,main,,0000,0000,0000,,We were just asking her out ourselves...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.48,0:06:48.10,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe next time, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.97,0:06:51.82,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.38,0:06:55.06,main,,0000,0000,0000,,See you tomorrow then, Gokou-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.52,0:07:00.30,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Should I have kept quiet?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.29,0:07:18.46,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Speaking of which, have you picked a club yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.46,0:07:19.92,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not joining one.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.92,0:07:22.60,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I have enough on my plate already.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.39,0:07:25.89,note,,0000,0000,0000,,Game Research Club
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.88,0:07:32.80,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't know we had a club like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.65,0:07:36.24,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Please give it a try if you'd like.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.12,0:07:40.03,main,,0000,0000,0000,,This looks like a "danmaku" shooter...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.03,0:07:42.68,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks pretty hard, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.68,0:07:48.29,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Our club president made it with the idea that it'd be some sort of entry test.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.29,0:07:51.21,main,,0000,0000,0000,,There's an easy mode, so give it a go.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.21,0:07:53.22,main,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.16,0:07:57.50,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and clear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.50,0:08:00.06,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Piece of cake for you, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.45,0:08:03.09,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine then.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.40,0:08:12.54,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That mode is seriously hard, you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.58,0:08:30.41,main,,0000,0000,0000,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.28,0:08:34.41,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You beat the high score too!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.92,0:08:39.29,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It was a thoroughly terrible game from beginning to end.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.29,0:08:41.73,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Please tell the creator to go die.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.46,0:08:43.70,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.70,0:08:46.46,main,,0000,0000,0000,,U-Um... won't you join our club?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.71,0:08:48.24,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Not interested.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.14,0:08:52.62,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.23,0:09:22.23,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It has nothing to do with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.97,0:09:26.95,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I just don't have time to go out with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.95,0:09:31.04,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You say that, but you've been spending a lot of time here lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.04,0:09:34.53,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I believe what Miss Kuroneko wants to say is,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.93,0:09:39.76,main,,0000,0000,0000,,"I'd rather be with you than go out with my classmates!"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.00,0:09:45.07,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't interpret things so weirdly!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.07,0:09:46.83,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't say a thing!!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.91,0:09:52.36,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, you can't go on like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.34,0:09:55.59,main,,0000,0000,0000,,How pushy can you get?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.59,0:09:57.56,main,,0000,0000,0000,,"You don't have any friends, right?"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.56,0:10:00.41,main,,0000,0000,0000,,"I'll help you out!"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.05,0:10:04.09,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What Mr. Kyousuke is thinking is,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.53,0:10:07.59,main,,0000,0000,0000,,"I'll show my cute kouhai how cool I can be!"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.00,0:10:11.32,main,,0000,0000,0000,,"And then she'll pay me back with sexual favors!"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.13,0:10:14.39,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of translation is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.26,0:10:18.16,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What are you planning to do to me??
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.16,0:10:18.92,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing!!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.92,0:10:20.67,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't hide behind my sheets!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.02,0:10:26.70,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, not all of it is untrue.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.70,0:10:29.32,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I like it when you call me "senpai",
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.32,0:10:35.40,main,,0000,0000,0000,,and I was thinking maybe if I help you out somehow, we could get to know each other better...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.40,0:10:38.93,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So I won't say I had zero ulterior motives,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.93,0:10:43.69,main,,0000,0000,0000,,but I really do want to help you solve your problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.69,0:10:46.14,main,,0000,0000,0000,,And that's not a lie!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.17,0:10:51.70,main,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, how about joining a club?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.69,0:10:59.69,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome to the Game Research Club!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.07,0:11:02.71,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Makabe, a second year.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.04,0:11:05.00,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Kousaka, third year,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.00,0:11:06.89,main,,0000,0000,0000,,and this is Gokou, first year.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.84,0:11:09.89,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me introduce you to our club president.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.89,0:11:11.18,main,,0000,0000,0000,,This way.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.80,0:11:14.15,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all guys here...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.26,0:11:20.47,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, that's OniPan...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.12,0:11:23.18,main,,0000,0000,0000,,President!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.18,0:11:25.98,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Kousaka-san and Gokou-san have come to visit.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.98,0:11:27.92,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, good work.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.98,0:11:31.86,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahhh!! Give me back my bike!!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.20,0:11:33.46,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.55,0:11:35.16,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.06,0:11:39.52,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So you put my little Fana-tan model to good use?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.81,0:11:41.94,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess it was worth it then.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.94,0:11:45.04,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I've kept it safe in my garage.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.04,0:11:46.64,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go pick it up later then.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.64,0:11:48.36,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry again...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.36,0:11:51.12,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't get your name or address at the time,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.12,0:11:53.47,main,,0000,0000,0000,,so I searched around Akiba afterwards, but..
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.85,0:11:55.37,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.37,0:12:00.52,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That night was so full of passion for us, it wasn't the time or place for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.81,0:12:08.91,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, I'm great buddies with this guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.91,0:12:10.47,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Kousaka-senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.47,0:12:13.17,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure you've noticed, so let me explain.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.17,0:12:16.10,main,,0000,0000,0000,,This guy's been held back who knows how many years now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.10,0:12:18.19,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why he looks so old.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.19,0:12:19.14,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.14,0:12:21.50,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't just go telling people that!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.50,0:12:22.51,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's embarrassing!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.85,0:12:25.86,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Forget the embarrassment and just hurry up and graduate!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.48,0:12:31.69,main,,0000,0000,0000,,We make games, but not everyone participates.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.98,0:12:37.65,main,,0000,0000,0000,,We have a lot of inactive members, and the only ones who come regularly are me and these guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.75,0:12:39.26,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yo.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.80,0:12:44.25,main,,0000,0000,0000,,We're holding a welcoming party soon, so I'll introduce everyone again then.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.71,0:12:46.98,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of games do you make?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.98,0:12:48.61,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Just shooters?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.61,0:12:50.31,main,,0000,0000,0000,,No, we make anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.39,0:12:52.98,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What tools do you use?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.98,0:12:55.25,main,,0000,0000,0000,,We should have anything you'd need.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.25,0:12:57.57,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Equipment, software, books...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.57,0:12:59.02,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Technical ones, that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.02,0:13:01.57,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You're welcome to borrow anything you need.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.25,0:13:05.60,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You're interested in making games?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.60,0:13:06.61,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you specialize in?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.61,0:13:08.06,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you write scripts?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.06,0:13:09.20,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you draw?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.20,0:13:09.83,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Music?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.83,0:13:11.16,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Storyboarding?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.58,0:13:19.71,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'm pretty much able to use any of the tools without instruction.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.40,0:13:24.34,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I take a look?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.34,0:13:25.80,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Go ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.99,0:13:31.15,main,,0000,0000,0000,,With her and Akagi-san, our new members this year are pretty high level.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.93,0:13:32.99,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Akagi?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.99,0:13:34.07,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.07,0:13:38.33,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Akagi Sena-san, a first year, like Gokou-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.33,0:13:42.19,main,,0000,0000,0000,,She actually had the highest score on that game before Gokou-san came along.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.27,0:13:44.68,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.37,0:13:46.95,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Akagi...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.95,0:13:48.94,main,,0000,0000,0000,,She isn't here today?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.33,0:13:50.43,main,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.90,0:13:56.42,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Even when she's here, it's like she's having a staring contest with the computers and books, so she doesn't really talk about games at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.42,0:14:00.82,main,,0000,0000,0000,,And we don't have any girls in the club, so I guess it's a bit awkward for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.01,0:14:06.23,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's another reason why it'd be great to have Gokou-san join us.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.37,0:14:12.23,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I guess it's better than having absolutely no girls in the club...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.04,0:14:14.24,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.24,0:14:15.61,main,,0000,0000,0000,,How about giving it a try?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.17,0:14:20.91,main,,0000,0000,0000,,They have tools and software I don't, and it seems I have freedom to do what I want to an extent,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.26,0:14:26.29,main,,0000,0000,0000,,so I suppose it's a bit more convenient than doing everything at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,main,,0000,0000,0000,,{eyecatch}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.92,0:14:38.34,main,,0000,0000,0000,,How's the club going for Kuroneko-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.34,0:14:41.37,main,,0000,0000,0000,,She doesn't make any trouble when she drops by.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.15,0:14:47.21,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You in charge of cleaning today?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.70,0:14:48.87,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.71,0:14:52.09,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What about everyone else?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.76,0:14:55.80,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.65,0:14:57.42,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Later then.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.47,0:15:00.14,main,,0000,0000,0000,,K-Kyou-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.42,0:15:19.63,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You're always so kind, Kyou-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.91,0:15:29.53,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.15,0:15:33.56,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Cleaning.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.07,0:15:35.73,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.73,0:15:37.56,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you trying to take pity on me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.82,0:15:40.09,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.67,0:15:45.14,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not lying when you say you're worried about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.08,0:15:47.34,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You said that, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.34,0:15:49.70,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. It's no lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.27,0:15:54.24,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand. You're not lying.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.85,0:15:57.13,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It isn't a lie,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.46,0:16:02.61,main,,0000,0000,0000,,but have you thought about where those feelings come from?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.43,0:16:06.36,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I'd refrain from telling you,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.35,0:16:13.39,main,,0000,0000,0000,,but the reason you're trying to help me is because your sister isn't around for you to help anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.99,0:16:18.67,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You're doing this because I'm a girl, younger than you, and I look like I'm having trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.67,0:16:21.93,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I look like I would rely on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.93,0:16:23.45,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's all there is to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.96,0:16:27.32,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not a replacement for your sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.32,0:16:29.09,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't insult me like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.75,0:16:40.91,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Kuroneko may have turned down joining a club and her classmates' invitations for the same reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.87,0:16:46.87,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Basically, she's afraid of losing time spent with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.63,0:16:54.52,main,,0000,0000,0000,,She has many things to do after school, and because she valued her time with us so much,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.52,0:16:57.68,main,,0000,0000,0000,,she may have been shunned by her class.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.22,0:17:05.66,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If you put yourself in her shoes and think about it, it's not so unexpected that she'd say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.61,0:17:09.69,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry, she'll forgive you if you apologize properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.24,0:17:12.52,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.52,0:17:14.15,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.15,0:17:15.71,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So, what will you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.35,0:17:19.89,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going to stop sticking your nose in her business now?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.63,0:17:26.67,main,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,main,,0000,0000,0000,,{Sign: Game Research Welcome Party ❤Yay!❤}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.81,0:17:29.50,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.50,0:17:31.12,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like you're all here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.50,0:17:35.10,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Then let's get this welcoming party started!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.35,0:17:38.47,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's make this year a blast as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.47,0:17:39.86,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Cheers!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.86,0:17:41.14,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Cheers!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.16,0:17:47.41,main,,0000,0000,0000,,We've got some good new members this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.41,0:17:48.46,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.46,0:17:50.34,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Good work, Makabe.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.27,0:17:53.60,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.14,0:17:55.82,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.57,0:18:04.64,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.64,0:18:06.91,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Kousaka, third year.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.25,0:18:10.07,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello. Akagi, first year.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.07,0:18:11.97,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Akagi?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.90,0:18:14.24,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.24,0:18:18.23,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you just don't look like you're having fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.51,0:18:22.92,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really like this club.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.92,0:18:24.34,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.34,0:18:25.53,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Just look.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.33,0:18:28.77,main,,0000,0000,0000,,They're all gross guys, and it's filthy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.77,0:18:31.54,main,,0000,0000,0000,,They make such weird games all the time, it's ridiculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.54,0:18:35.74,main,,0000,0000,0000,,And bringing in all these adult games and figures is just absurd.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.27,0:18:38.26,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Then why did you join?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.09,0:18:43.03,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to learn how to program.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.03,0:18:48.39,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The president's game, putting aside the setting, was well-made.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.39,0:18:51.48,main,,0000,0000,0000,,And the equipment here is better than expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.48,0:18:56.02,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought there might be enough benefits despite all the problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.54,0:18:59.29,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I've heard this story somewhere before...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.29,0:19:03.02,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But my patience does have its limits.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.02,0:19:09.30,main,,0000,0000,0000,,There are only a few people in here that actually participate, and the room is plain filthy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.72,0:19:15.76,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You look more like the kind to join the student council than the Game Research Club.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.13,0:19:17.91,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What a relief.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.91,0:19:20.81,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to be thought of as one of their kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.09,0:19:26.87,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But won't you get branded as an otaku by joining a club like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.51,0:19:31.88,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure people will understand if I explain myself properly!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.88,0:19:39.34,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Recent anime have girls trying to hide their otaku hobbies, but those are all just exaggerations.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.34,0:19:42.60,main,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no condemnation like that in reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.21,0:19:46.66,main,,0000,0000,0000,,We live in an age where watching anime in theaters is perfectly normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.66,0:19:49.34,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But aren't eroge and doujinshi too much for them?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.34,0:19:51.21,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course they are!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.21,0:19:54.99,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's always important to pay attention to the time, place, and occasion, and the situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.99,0:19:57.41,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Otaku aren't avoided because of their hobbies themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.41,0:20:01.32,main,,0000,0000,0000,,They're avoided when they do something socially unacceptable.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.85,0:20:06.47,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Like the ones who spew lines and catchphrases anywhere and everywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.47,0:20:08.14,main,,0000,0000,0000,,They're the worst.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.04,0:20:13.86,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds like some runt that can only live by leeching off others is trying to talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.38,0:20:17.44,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, Gokou-san, you were there?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.44,0:20:20.60,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You leave such a weak impression, I didn't notice you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.60,0:20:23.38,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You two know each other?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.38,0:20:26.19,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The most annoying woman in the class.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.99,0:20:29.53,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The biggest problem child in the class.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.74,0:20:44.73,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I should confirm...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.48,0:20:46.39,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.80,0:20:48.71,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.17,0:20:54.80,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You said you were interested in programming, but don't you like games?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.70,0:20:57.85,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I like them as much as anyone else...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.85,0:20:59.14,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.43,0:21:03.41,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If you didn't, you wouldn't be so good at them.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.81,0:21:06.04,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It just kind of sounded like an act.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.67,0:21:09.53,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it half is.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.53,0:21:10.80,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.52,0:21:19.32,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not something I need to hide, but I want to be a game designer in the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.67,0:21:20.94,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.94,0:21:23.33,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's why you want to learn how to program.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.07,0:21:26.32,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess that's how it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.61,0:21:28.65,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So you like games that much?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.65,0:21:30.91,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I like them a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.91,0:21:32.74,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Playing them and making them.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.74,0:21:34.93,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you played "Homoge Club"?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.93,0:21:37.85,main,,0000,0000,0000,,YES!! That game is godly, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.69,0:21:47.09,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Please forget I said that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.51,0:21:49.95,main,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's already ringing...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.95,0:21:51.60,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Very clearly.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.17,0:21:58.85,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it. You're Akagi's sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.85,0:21:59.41,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The fujo—
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.02,0:22:02.02,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Wh-What are you saying?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.02,0:22:03.61,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't understand...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.19,0:22:05.85,main,,0000,0000,0000,,My, my.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.43,0:22:08.11,main,,0000,0000,0000,,How unexpected.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.11,0:22:10.57,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That you would have such tastes...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.30,0:22:14.88,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm telling you, I'm not!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.88,0:22:20.92,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I've only heard about it, but I hear Maschera's getting pretty popular lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.92,0:22:22.58,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What might you be talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.58,0:22:23.81,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm afraid I don't understand...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.03,0:22:27.27,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't bother playing dumb.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.27,0:22:32.35,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You were shrieking in joy those nights fantasizing about that Shin x Luci coupling.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.24,0:22:35.11,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You fool!!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.49,0:22:40.09,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That cute seme x tsundere uke of Luci x Shin is the essence of Maschera!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.09,0:22:41.79,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Reversing that coupling?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.79,0:22:42.84,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.84,0:22:44.89,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You fake!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.89,0:22:47.25,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.25,0:22:50.82,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the one coupling that can never be reversed.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.32,0:22:52.30,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.10,0:22:55.35,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It would seem I've made you trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.37,0:23:03.89,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You tricked me!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.04,0:23:06.86,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.47,0:23:11.95,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.30,0:23:14.13,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I like homos.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.72,0:23:16.90,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I am completely rotten!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.34,0:23:19.91,main,,0000,0000,0000,,My, is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.91,0:23:25.16,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're so rotten, then I'm sure you can even fantasize about half-real things like the Prince of Tennis musical?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.16,0:23:27.06,main,,0000,0000,0000,,With the greatest ease.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.06,0:23:31.28,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Half-real or two-dimensional or inanimate!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.28,0:23:35.78,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So long as they brush against my heartstrings, I can save them in my mind and fantasize.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.78,0:23:41.57,main,,0000,0000,0000,,As an extreme example, I can take a fork and spoon and draw out some form of love.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.57,0:23:43.92,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I commend your confidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.92,0:23:46.86,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But do you even fantasize about real men?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.48,0:23:50.15,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I have nothing to hide!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.15,0:23:55.74,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Last night, I had a dream where Makabe-senpai was gang raped by the other club members!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.70,0:24:01.53,main,,0000,0000,0000,,This exceeds my calculations...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.53,0:24:04.40,main,,0000,0000,0000,,To think that she held such evil within her...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.79,0:24:05.96,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Makabe!!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.96,0:24:08.94,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You've reeled in an absolutely terrifying pervert into our club!!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.20,0:24:13.01,main,,0000,0000,0000,,No!!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.00,0:24:16.00,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry Makabe-senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.00,0:24:19.00,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry I fantasized about you and the president going out!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.00,0:24:24.65,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But I couldn't hear your polite tsukkomi as anything but being tsundere!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.65,0:24:25.71,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.71,0:24:28.43,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't cause him any deeper trauma than you already have!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.79,0:24:31.72,main,,0000,0000,0000,,No!!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.72,0:24:33.93,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I did it again!!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.02,0:24:35.70,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Just kill me!!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.70,0:24:37.72,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Kill me!!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.72,0:24:39.52,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Kill me!! Kill me!!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.68,0:24:45.81,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm done for!! I'm—!!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.81,0:24:48.50,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Kill me now!! What are you looking at?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.50,0:24:49.73,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What's up, Kousaka?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.73,0:24:53.43,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Your sister's gone mad! What do we do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.28,0:25:00.87,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell her, "Sena-chan, you're so cute! Sena-chan, it's not your fault!" until she calms down.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.75,0:25:03.31,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.31,0:25:05.04,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You're screwed in the head, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.00,0:25:07.29,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine, let me talk to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.29,0:25:08.63,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll calm her down.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.70,0:25:17.13,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do that...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.66,0:25:18.93,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.93,0:25:20.77,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, Onii-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.68,0:25:28.94,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Um... Sorry to show you such a scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.94,0:25:31.07,main,,0000,0000,0000,,No, that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.09,0:25:34.27,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, not really okay, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.19,0:25:43.74,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.84,0:25:46.78,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.29,0:25:49.55,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll admit it.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.03,0:25:53.73,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I was lonely without my sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.74,0:25:55.68,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.50,0:26:00.32,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Even with the way she is, it's pretty lonely without her.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.65,0:26:02.98,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.05,0:26:07.41,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You know...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.92,0:26:10.18,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm worried about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.60,0:26:14.79,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So, I'm going to keep sticking my nose in your business.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.99,0:26:23.76,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Do what you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.36,0:26:27.81,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I've already given up.
