Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.98,0:01:16.12,op-kan,,0000,0000,0000,,そんな優しくしないで　どんな顔すればいいの？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.12,0:01:19.42,op-kan,,0000,0000,0000,,積み重ねた言葉で　
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.42,0:01:26.47,op-kan,,0000,0000,0000,,見えないよ　きみの横顔
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.47,0:01:38.61,op-kan,,0000,0000,0000,,どこだっけ？　なくした鍵は見つからないままで
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.61,0:01:45.25,op-kan,,0000,0000,0000,,ため息...すれ違いに意地張って疲れちゃう
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.25,0:01:52.02,op-kan,,0000,0000,0000,,ほんの少し近く　きみとの距離が
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.02,0:01:59.23,op-kan,,0000,0000,0000,,うまく掴めないんだ　あとちょっとなのに!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.23,0:02:06.44,op-kan,,0000,0000,0000,,そんな優しくしないで　ほら　また傷つけあって
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.44,0:02:13.28,op-kan,,0000,0000,0000,,積み重ねたウソでもう　動けなくなってる
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.28,0:02:20.62,op-kan,,0000,0000,0000,,すぐに会いに行きたいけど　言葉は見つからないし
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.62,0:02:31.13,op-kan,,0000,0000,0000,,最後の一ページくらい　きみには笑顔見せたい
Comment: 0,0:02:51.08,0:02:53.05,main,,0000,0000,0000,,{Romaji}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.98,0:01:16.12,op-rom,,0000,0000,0000,,sonna yasashiku shinai de donna kao sureba ii no?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.12,0:01:19.42,op-rom,,0000,0000,0000,,tsumikasaneta kotoba de
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.42,0:01:26.47,op-rom,,0000,0000,0000,,mienai yo kimi no yokogao
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.47,0:01:38.61,op-rom,,0000,0000,0000,,dokodakke? nakushita kagi ha mitsukaranai mama de
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.61,0:01:45.25,op-rom,,0000,0000,0000,,tameiki... surechigai ni iji hatte tsukarechau
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.25,0:01:52.02,op-rom,,0000,0000,0000,,hon no sukoshi chikaku kimi to no kyori ga
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.02,0:01:59.23,op-rom,,0000,0000,0000,,umaku tsukamenainda ato chotto na no ni
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.23,0:02:06.44,op-rom,,0000,0000,0000,,sonna yasashikushinaide hora mata kizutsukeatte
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.44,0:02:13.28,op-rom,,0000,0000,0000,,tsumikasaneta uso de mou ugokenakunatteru
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.28,0:02:20.62,op-rom,,0000,0000,0000,,sugu ni ai ni ikitai kedo kotoba ha mitsukaranai shi
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.62,0:02:31.13,op-rom,,0000,0000,0000,,saigo no ichi pe-ji kurai kimi ni ha egao misetai
Comment: 0,0:01:08.11,0:01:08.11,main,,0000,0000,0000,,{Translation}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.98,0:01:16.12,op-eng,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be so nice to me, I just don't know how to react
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.12,0:01:19.42,op-eng,,0000,0000,0000,,With all these words piling up,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.42,0:01:26.47,op-eng,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't even see your face
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.47,0:01:38.61,op-eng,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is it? I lost my key, now I can't find it
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.61,0:01:45.25,op-eng,,0000,0000,0000,,Sigh, I'll burn out if I keep acting like this whenever we fight
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.25,0:01:52.02,op-eng,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe we're close? I just can't figure out
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.02,0:01:59.23,op-eng,,0000,0000,0000,,Just how far away I am, even though you're right there
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.23,0:02:06.44,op-eng,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be so nice to me, see? We hurt each other again
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.44,0:02:13.28,op-eng,,0000,0000,0000,,With all these lies piling up, I can't even move
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.28,0:02:20.62,op-eng,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to see you now, but I don't know what to say
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.62,0:02:31.13,op-eng,,0000,0000,0000,,If this is the end for our story, I want you to see my smile
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,main,,0000,0000,0000,,< ED >
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.73,0:27:01.34,ed_romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,houkago chaimu ha anata shiru mahou de
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.34,0:27:07.36,ed_romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,tayorinai senaka mo itooshiku saseru no
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.93,0:27:14.54,ed_romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,uchigawa gara kacchari kagi kaketa kimochi ni
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.54,0:27:19.58,ed_romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,kidzuite hoshii dake bukiyou na ai
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.98,0:27:24.02,ed_romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,dore dake omoeba todoku no?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.02,0:27:27.40,ed_romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,senyou ni kaita kimochi
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.40,0:27:34.73,ed_romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,namida mata koboshi makura nurasu no
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.79,0:27:38.25,ed_romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,shosen koi saredo koi
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.25,0:27:41.56,ed_romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,hajirau kashikosa ha jama na dake
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.56,0:27:48.95,ed_romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,mujaki na kokoro no mama yudanetai no
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.95,0:27:52.33,ed_romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,anata nara dakishimeru?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.33,0:27:54.79,ed_romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,sore tomo koi kogare machibouke?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.79,0:28:03.01,ed_romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,matenai! inochi mijikashi otome ha
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{ED Kanji}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.73,0:27:01.34,ed_kanji,,0000,0000,0000,,放課後チャイムは　あなた知る魔法で
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.34,0:27:07.36,ed_kanji,,0000,0000,0000,,頼りない背中も　愛おしくさせるの
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.93,0:27:14.54,ed_kanji,,0000,0000,0000,,内側から「カッチャリ」　鍵かけた気持ちに
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.54,0:27:19.58,ed_kanji,,0000,0000,0000,,気付いて欲しいだけ　不器用な愛
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.98,0:27:24.02,ed_kanji,,0000,0000,0000,,どれだけ想えば　届くの？
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.02,0:27:27.40,ed_kanji,,0000,0000,0000,,千葉に書いた気持ち
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.40,0:27:34.73,ed_kanji,,0000,0000,0000,,涙　また零し　枕濡らすの
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.79,0:27:38.25,ed_kanji,,0000,0000,0000,,しょせん恋　されど恋
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.25,0:27:41.56,ed_kanji,,0000,0000,0000,,恥じらう　賢さは　邪魔なだけ
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.56,0:27:48.95,ed_kanji,,0000,0000,0000,,子供な心のまま委ねたいの
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.95,0:27:52.33,ed_kanji,,0000,0000,0000,,あなたなら抱きしめる？　それとも
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.33,0:27:54.79,ed_kanji,,0000,0000,0000,,恋い焦がれ　待ち惚け？
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.79,0:28:03.01,ed_kanji,,0000,0000,0000,,待てない！　命短し乙女は
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{ED Translation}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.73,0:27:01.34,ed_english,,0000,0000,0000,,The last bell rings, and the magic of knowing you
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.34,0:27:07.36,ed_english,,0000,0000,0000,,Makes your unreliable self all more sweeter
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.93,0:27:14.54,ed_english,,0000,0000,0000,,From the inside a click-clack, locking away my feelings
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.54,0:27:19.58,ed_english,,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to see, a clumsy love
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.98,0:27:24.02,ed_english,,0000,0000,0000,,How much must I desire for them to reach?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.02,0:27:27.40,ed_english,,0000,0000,0000,,These feelings, written on one thousand leaves
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.40,0:27:34.73,ed_english,,0000,0000,0000,,Tears, spilled again, wet my pillow
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.79,0:27:38.25,ed_english,,0000,0000,0000,,All it is is love, but then it is love
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.25,0:27:41.56,ed_english,,0000,0000,0000,,Knowing all this shame just gets in my way
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.56,0:27:48.95,ed_english,,0000,0000,0000,,I just want to blur with this innocent heart
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.95,0:27:52.33,ed_english,,0000,0000,0000,,You might hold me tight, or maybe
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.33,0:27:54.79,ed_english,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m too deeply in love, waiting in vain
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.79,0:28:03.01,ed_english,,0000,0000,0000,,I won’t wait! A maiden’s life is but so short
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,main,,0000,0000,0000,,< Preview >
